data.title: Report: Memphis Grizzlies trade David Roddy to Phoenix Suns - Memphis Local, Sports, Business & Food News
data.meta_description: The Grizzlies trade David Roddy as part of a three-team swap. Memphis brings back, for the moment, Japanese forward Yuta Watanabe.
